Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 years have passed since the \NWar of the Best in Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew each \Ncompleted individual training
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returned on Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to go on to the next stage the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nobody has arrived yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the poster once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says "At least 70 million berries bounty."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna deal with \Ncaptains with less bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only say it once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match for me so I'm \Nnot gonna drink with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure Kill: Green Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."Devil"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, young lady, do you wanna drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a skeleton, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a real man--Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come back from hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook's concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats' recruitment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be sailing out soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did it hit you? Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Explosive Situation! \NLuffy vs. Fake Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Sabaody Archipelago in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, we have to say goodbye here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them discover our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put this on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that! That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in case something happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you hide your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world thinks that you're dead but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...people know what you \Nlook like from 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cause trouble, you \Nwon't be able to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the backpack, I put 50 extra \Nchanges of clothes, 1000 lunches,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,handkerchiefs and tissues,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5 years' worth of towels, 3 years' \Nworth of water and snacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,silverware, toothbrushes, soap,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hand creams and 3 years' worth \Nof bug bite ointment and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you can meet your friends safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard Sabaody has \Nbecome unsafe these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's why the Navy is paying a \Nlot of attention to what goes on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take extra care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need us, we Kuja Pirates \Nwill always come to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And could you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm not gonna marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just want you to leave \Nwithout saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've never said it to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See you!\N--Take care, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wants to see me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it what they call...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a proposal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been told by Hancock \Nnot to cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hit me on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:58.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GROVE #13 SHAKKY'S RIP-OFF BAR
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stupid swordsman got here first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our new voyage will be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Franky-chan came \Nsecond, about 10 days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went out to see the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny is alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course--there isn't even a \Nscratch and the coating is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no regret for honorable wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! A year to heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had such \Na strong sense of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Duval.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you think I'm handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I returned your favor, young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even on rainy days and windy days,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dangerous pirates tried to steal that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I fought day after day \Neven with cuts and bruises!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was very painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duval-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, how did you get hurt so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fall for me... I mean, \Nlisten to me, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's because the Navy finally...\N--And Nami-chan came third...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went out shopping to kill time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No interest in my story anymore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san's shopping! Nami-san's shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-chan came fourth 3 \Ndays ago and went to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper-chan came fifth yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook-chan has a concert \Ntoday on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So 7 members including you have \Nalready arrived on this archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen Nico Robin and Luffy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's extremely difficult \Njust to get to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys are all quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you can meet them soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But I can't believe \Nthat you trained Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be incredibly strong now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him for 6 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see his progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Progress...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of progress Nami-san made!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Young master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I endured 2 years of arduous training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to shake off any sign \Nof seduction and show my results!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,GROVE #47
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some thugs are fighting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that the pirates would \Nsettle down after Whitebeard died...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming from everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the whole island has become lawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard, Kid, and Drake are doing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever they want in the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're the ones who'll \Nfollow... I mean, beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, look!\N--Th-They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What they say was true as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were thought to be dead fighting \Nagainst the Navy 2 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they showed up again on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and they're the most powerful \Npirate group on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is it Nami?! Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The Straw Hats...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pirate Hunter" Zoro. A \N120 million berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Black Foot" Sanji. A \N77 million berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She obtained a bounty at \Nthe age of 8. Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An 80 million berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a cotton-candy lover--Tony Tony Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 50 berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:12:01.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"THE STRAW HATS" ZORO SANJI ROBIN CHOPPER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is there? Is Luffy there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a good match for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you stopping us, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we cause trouble with them, \NStraw Hat Luffy won't keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not wise to have an \Nunnecessary conflict before
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we go to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that talking racoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Racoons can't talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you got here first, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe you didn't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji and Robin, you guys finally made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've never seen something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might cause us trouble. Ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our target, Nico Robin, \Nis a Devil Fruit eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be painful if she fights back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's catch her off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better hurry up. I wonder \Nif they're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Nami-san and Robin-chan \Nto try my improved food soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, I better go see if \Nthe kitchen in the Sunny is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, go food shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hit me knowing who I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it? You made me look like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You humiliated me in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an elite pirate with \Na 400 million bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kneel down on the ground in fear now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and beg for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he wanna live?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you realize now how \Naudacious your actions were!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're so scared \Nthat you can't even talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few moments ago, a man who \Nhas a long nose and a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with long hair messed with us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so our captain is in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better apologize now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kneel on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you're gonna throw away \Nyour life with just one mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain pulls his trigger very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kneel on the ground already! \NHe's Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to get killed? Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did he do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock was right. I should put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! Sanji! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally see each other \Nbut you're acting weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and Sanji, you guys did \Npretty well in these 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why aren't you guys talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he's still following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're being shy, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that racoon knows about us \Nthe Straw Hats a bit too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about that, \Ntoo, but maybe... Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real cotton-candy lover--Chopper, \Na 50 berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's their pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys changed a little. But I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was abandoned on this island before
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they died and he's been living in the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks his masters are back \Nand that's why he's following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get rid of that \Nfox and take him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the pet looks the same as the \Nposter, we'd look more authentic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna keep him? What does he eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like cotton candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need you anymore! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cucumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! Robin, you're scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hey, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a crisis! Robin has been abducted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't we tell Captain Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Did you guys see Luffy already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have new members by now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we better rescue Robin already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me there with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sabaody! We caught Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a fox kind of thing \Nthat won't let go of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky was all fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to worry about the Sunny now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I have to do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viva Sabaody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I gotta focus on cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get the best ingredients first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And cook something really good that'll \Nsurprise Nami-san and Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you might want to check the \Nshop on the beach at Grove #42...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you! I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, fisherman, sell me some \Nfish at your best price!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nobody's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you the owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The green-haired man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Green-haired? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did something horrible! \NIt happened just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, I wanna fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man, you don't look \Nlike a fishing type of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to meet friends on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I got here first and I \Ndon't see any of them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take me out to \Nsea on your fishing boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll take you out on that \Nboat right there so go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Green hair, 3 swords, and a belly warmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and he has a deep scar on his eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scar on his eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, this is the guy! Is he your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I only know him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to get on the fishing boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I came back here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, young man, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! We're gonna set \Nsail for the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we've been dreaming of!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wake up, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the wrong ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think he's heading for \Nthe Fish-Man Island like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was unlike him to show up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he'd do something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pirate ship! Maybe they'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it's okay. It's \Nnot your fault at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't die. We're lucky \Nto know where he's heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, can I have some fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the water! Something is surfacing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a galleon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't coated well and was \Ncrushed by water pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or attacked by Sea Kings?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like it's been \Ncut by some kind of knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could cut a ship this big?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you ruin our dream \Nto go to the New World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a quirk of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should blame your own fate that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,brought a plague onto your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:22:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's back! I couldn't \Ncare less about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.21,0:23:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the wrong ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats are gathering
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the Sunny, preparing for departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Marines caught wind of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out for the Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent who cornered \NLuffy & Co. two years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is targetting them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Navy Has Set Out! The \NStraw Hats in Danger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
